HEADWORD: Four
<hw>Four</hw> <pr>(f⟦omac⟧r)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[OE.
<ets>four</ets>, <ets>fower</ets>, <ets>feower</ets>, AS.
<ets>fe⟦oacute⟧wer</ets>; akin to OS. <ets>fiwar</ets>, D. & G.
<ets>vier</ets>, OHG. <ets>fior</ets>, Icel. <ets>fj⟦omac⟧rir</ets>, Sw.
